description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 12, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 36, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Box for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80123-84114-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [36 Votes, Common]
